addGroup(address).details: Allows owner to add a group of pools (a factory)

dragoCount().details: Provides the total number of registered pools

drain().details: Allows owner to collect fees by draining the balance

getFee().details: Provides the fee required to register a pool
getFee().return: Number of the fee in wei

getGroups().details: Provides the addresses of the groups/factories
getGroups().return: Array of addresses of the groups

getNameFromAddress(address).details: Provides a pool's name from its address

getSymbolFromAddress(address).details: Provides a pool's symbol from its address

register(address,string,string,uint256,a.details: Allows a factory which is an authority to register a pool

setFee(uint256).details: Allows owner to set a fee to register pools

params._fee: Value of the fee in wei

setMeta(uint256,bytes32,bytes32).details: Allows pool owner to set metadata for a pool

setUpgraded(uint256).details: Allows owner to update version on registry upgrade

unregister(uint256).details: Allows owner to unregister a pool

updateOwner(uint256).details: Allows anyone to update the owner in the registry

updateOwners(uint256[]).details: Allows anyone to update many owners if they differ from registered

upgrade(address).details: Allows owner to create a new registry.When the registry gets upgraded, a migration of all funds is required
